## TL;DR Cheat Sheet

| Device        | Main Job                  |
| ------------- | ------------------------- |
| Modem         | Connects you to ISP       |
| Router        | Directs traffic + NAT     |
| Switch        | Fast local communication  |
| Hub           | Obsolete broadcast device |
| Firewall      | Security gatekeeper       |
| Load Balancer | Traffic distribution      |

NAT - LET all devices on the router to share one public ip.
